#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:1 of
msgid "Matrix or vector norm."
msgstr "矩阵或向量范数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:3 of
msgid ""
"This function is able to return one of eight different matrix norms, or "
"one of an infinite number of vector norms (described below), depending on"
" the value of the ``ord`` parameter."
msgstr ""
"此函数能够根据 ``ord`` 参数的值返回八种不同的矩阵范数之一，或无限多种向量"
"范数之一（如下所述）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:7 of
msgid "Input tensor.  If `axis` is None, `x` must be 1-D or 2-D."
msgstr "输入张量。如果 `axis` 为 None，则 `x` 必须是一维或二维。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:9 of
msgid ""
"Order of the norm (see table under ``Notes``). inf means maxframe "
"tensor's `inf` object."
msgstr ""
"范数的阶数（参见 ``Notes`` 下的表格）。inf 表示 maxframe 张量的 `inf` "
"对象。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:12 of
msgid ""
"If `axis` is an integer, it specifies the axis of `x` along which to "
"compute the vector norms.  If `axis` is a 2-tuple, it specifies the axes "
"that hold 2-D matrices, and the matrix norms of these matrices are "
"computed.  If `axis` is None then either a vector norm (when `x` is 1-D) "
"or a matrix norm (when `x` is 2-D) is returned."
msgstr ""
"如果 `axis` 是一个整数，它指定计算向量范数时 `x` 的轴。如果 `axis` 是"
"一个二元组，它指定包含二维矩阵的轴，并计算这些矩阵的矩阵范数。如果 `axis`"
" 为 None，则返回向量范数（当 `x` 是一维时）或矩阵范数（当 `x` 是二维时）"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:18 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are normed over are left in the "
"result as dimensions with size one.  With this option the result will "
"broadcast correctly against the original `x`."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，范数计算所涉及的轴将保留在结果中，尺寸为 1。使用此选项时"
"，结果将可以正确地与原始 `x` 广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:23 of
msgid "**n** -- Norm of the matrix or vector(s)."
msgstr "**n** -- 矩阵或向量的范数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:28 of
msgid ""
"For values of ``ord <= 0``, the result is, strictly speaking, not a "
"mathematical 'norm', but it may still be useful for various numerical "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"对于 ``ord <= 0`` 的值，严格来说结果不是数学意义上的“范数”，但对各种"
"数值计算目的仍然可能有用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:32 of
msgid "The following norms can be calculated:"
msgstr "可以计算以下范数："

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:35 of
msgid "ord"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:35 of
msgid "norm for matrices"
msgstr "矩阵范数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:35 of
msgid "norm for vectors"
msgstr "向量范数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:37 of
msgid "None"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:37 maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:38 of
msgid "Frobenius norm"
msgstr "Frobenius 范数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:37 of
msgid "2-norm"
msgstr "2-范数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:38 of
msgid "'fro'"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:38 maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:39
#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:42 maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:47 of
msgid "--"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:39 of
msgid "'nuc'"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:39 of
msgid "nuclear norm"
msgstr "核范数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:40 of
msgid "inf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:40 of
msgid "max(sum(abs(x), axis=1))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:40 of
msgid "max(abs(x))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:41 of
msgid "-inf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:41 of
msgid "min(sum(abs(x), axis=1))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:41 of
msgid "min(abs(x))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:42 of
msgid "0"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:42 of
msgid "sum(x != 0)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:43 of
msgid "1"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:43 of
msgid "max(sum(abs(x), axis=0))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:43 maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:44
#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:45 maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:46 of
msgid "as below"
msgstr "如下所示"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:44 of
msgid "-1"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:44 of
msgid "min(sum(abs(x), axis=0))"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:45 of
msgid "2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:45 of
msgid "2-norm (largest sing. value)"
msgstr "2-范数（最大奇异值）"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:46 of
msgid "-2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:46 of
msgid "smallest singular value"
msgstr "最小奇异值"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:47 of
msgid "other"
msgstr "其他"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:47 of
msgid "sum(abs(x)**ord)**(1./ord)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:50 of
msgid "The Frobenius norm is given by [1]_:"
msgstr "Frobenius 范数由 [1]_ 给出："

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:52 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":math:`||A||_F = [\\\\sum_{i,j} abs(a_{i,j})^2]^{1/2}`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:54 of
msgid "The nuclear norm is the sum of the singular values."
msgstr "核范数是奇异值的和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:57 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.norm.norm:58 of
msgid ""
"G. H. Golub and C. F. Van Loan, *Matrix Computations*, Baltimore, MD, "
"Johns Hopkins University Press, 1985, pg. 15"
msgstr ""
"G. H. Golub 和 C. F. Van Loan，《矩阵计算》，巴尔的摩，马里兰州，"
"约翰霍普金斯大学出版社，1985年，第15页"

